Austin St. John https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Austin_St._John 0 Jason Geiger (born September 17, 1974 in Roswell, New Mexico, U.S.), professionally known as Austin St. John, is an American actor and martial artist. He is best known for his portrayal of Jason Lee Scott in the Power Rangers franchise.
